HEADWORD: Avulse
<hw>A*vulse"</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>avulsus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>avellere</ets> to tear off;
<ets>a</ets> (<ets>ab</ets>) + <ets>vellere</ets> to pluck.]</ety>
